"The wall" meme is an interesting one... in traditional slavic literature I've often encountering many authors talking about women "blossoming" with the age of thirty being a woman's peak. It's obvious that nowadays this is more rarely the case, but it is due to bad body care

the more abuse you put your body through (most fatal one is lack of sleep), like drugs, heavy chemical makeup, lots of alcohol, dehydration, bad diet etc. the faster you age, this is obviously true for both sexes ofc. But problem is people lead unhealthy lives and age too rapidly

Of course there is truth, men usually look good in deeper age, especially if they are physically active and have proper nutrition. But the fact that you will look good until your 40s is often a bad excuse, "cope", for wasting your youth. Make proper use of all seasons of ur life
